OL,3,C'Weak concrete' found in four schools
OL,4,Cafter ceiling collapse
OL,6,FWeak and brittle concrete has been
OL,7,Ffound in four schools on North
OL,8,FTyneside after a collapsed ceiling in
OL,9,Fone building sparked a council-wide
OL,10,Finvestigation.
OL,12,FNo one was injured when a chunk of
OL,13,Fconcrete fell through the ceiling
OL,14,Fovernight at Fordley Primary School in
OL,15,FAnnitsford last December, but the
OL,16,Fschool was forced to partially shut
OL,17,Fover safety fears.
