OL,3,C'Weak concrete' found in four schools
OL,4,Cafter ceiling collapse
OL,6,FAn investigation was launched after
OL,7,Fthe incident and found three other
OL,8,Fschools required further checks,
OL,9,Fforcing their partial closure in
OL,10,FFebruary.
OL,12,FThey were Churchill Community College
OL,13,Fin Wallsend, Hazlewood Primary School
OL,14,Fin Wideopen and Grasmere Academy in
OL,15,FKillingworth.
OL,17,FPupils at the affected sites have all
OL,18,Freturned to face-to-face teaching.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
