OL,3,C'Weak concrete' found in four schools
OL,4,Cafter ceiling collapse
OL,6,FMost of the children are being taught
OL,7,Fin parts of the school buildings that
OL,8,Fare unaffected, but some have been
OL,9,Ftaught in marquees or bussed to other
OL,10,Fschools.
OL,12,FNow, a structural report has found
OL,13,Fthat the issue was caused by a weak
OL,14,Fand brittle concrete mix, "Hollow
OL,15,FConcrete Block and Plank", used in
OL,16,Fsome blocks when the schools were
OL,17,Fconstructed in the 1960s.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
