OL,3,C'Weak concrete' found in four schools
OL,4,Cafter ceiling collapse
OL,6,FThe council said that when one block
OL,7,Fcracks, it forms a weakness,
OL,8,Fpotentially causing other blocks in
OL,9,Fthe same row to crack slowly over time.
OL,11,FIt does not create issues with
OL,12,Fstability for the whole building but
OL,13,Fdoes for isolated areas, it added.
OL,15,FIt is a different problem to that
OL,16,Fcaused by Reinforced Autoclaved
OL,17,FAerated Concrete (RAAC) which forced
OL,18,Fthe closure of hundreds of schools
OL,19,Facross the country in September 2023.
