OL,6,FThe authority is awaiting further
OL,7,Ftests from Churchill, Hazlewood and
OL,8,FGrasmere before reports are finalised.
OL,10,FIt will then work with the schools,
OL,11,Fthe Department for Education and
OL,12,Fstructural engineers on remedial works
OL,13,Fto allow the buildings to fully reopen.
OL,15,FIn the meantime, all students will
OL,16,Fcontinue face-to-face teaching in the
OL,17,Fcurrent arrangements until portable
OL,18,Fclassrooms arrive.
