OL,6,FJulie Firth, director of children's
OL,7,Fservices for North Tyneside Council,
OL,8,Fsaid: "I'd like to thank the
OL,9,Fcommunities at the affected schools
OL,10,Ffor their patience; we know this has
OL,11,Fbeen disruptive and difficult.
OL,13,F"We are so proud of how the pupils are
OL,14,Fadapting and carrying on with their
OL,15,Feducation, and that's testament to the
OL,16,Fhard work and dedication of the staff.
