OL,6,F"A lot of the short-term solutions
OL,7,Fwould not have been possible without
OL,8,Fthe coming together of the wider
OL,9,Fschool and education community across
OL,10,FNorth Tyneside, who have undertaken
OL,11,Fsome serious reshuffling to
OL,12,Ftemporarily host pupils and their
OL,13,Fteachers from other schools.
OL,15,F"We are working with the school
OL,16,Fleaders and the Department for
OL,17,FEducation on longer-term solutions".
